# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:100
translate spanish jez10_d38c3b2a:

    # det "How did you come across information like that? Was your dad involved?"
    det "¿Cómo has conseguido esa información? ¿Estaba tu padre metido en eso?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:101
translate spanish jez10_2e52ce55:

    # pc "No, it doesn't have anything to do with my dad, I don't think."
    pc "No, no tiene nada que ver con mi padre, no creo."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:108
translate spanish jez10_184fbca8:

    # pc "So, there's this girl I know. We hang out at the park together some nights."
    pc "Bueno, hay una chica que conozco. Algunas noches quedamos en el parque."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:109
translate spanish jez10_e1230383:

    # det "Isabel Walker?"
    det "¿Isabel Walker?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:110
translate spanish jez10_e3d4a760:

    # pc "Um... is that Izzy's full name? I'm not even sure."
    pc "Eh... ¿ese es el nombre completo de Izzy? Ni siquiera estoy seguro."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:111
translate spanish jez10_30709f8a:

    # det "Yeah, that's her. Okay, keep going."
    det "Sí, es ella. Vale, sigue."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:112
translate spanish jez10_3c61fd72:

    # pc "Well she asked me to deliver this package to her."
    pc "Bueno, me pidió que le entregara este paquete."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:118
translate spanish jez10_32965199:

    # det "You're delivering drugs for Isabel Walker?"
    det "¿Estás repartiendo drogas para Isabel Walker?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:119
translate spanish jez10_86b0a5be:

    # pc "No!"
    pc "¡No!"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:120
translate spanish jez10_7ff5772d:

    # pc "I mean, I might have, this one time. I didn't know what was in the package. And I haven't done it any other time."
    pc "Bueno, puede que lo haya hecho, esta única vez. No sabía lo que había en el paquete. Y no lo he vuelto a hacer."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:121
translate spanish jez10_c1715c95:

    # pc "I just wanted her to like me, you know?"
    pc "Solo quería caerle bien, ¿sabes?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:126
translate spanish jez10_7ed58a96:

    # det "Okay. Go on."
    det "Vale. Sigue."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:127
translate spanish jez10_ed948a44:

    # pc "So I took the package where she told me to deliver it."
    pc "Así que llevé el paquete donde me dijo que lo entregara."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:133
translate spanish jez10_ac4590db:

    # pc "There's this girl that I'm friends with. I think her brother might be involved. A guy named Mickey."
    pc "Hay una chica con la que soy amiga. Creo que su hermano podría estar metido en esto. Un chico llamado Mickey."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:134
translate spanish jez10_05814737:

    # det "Mickey? Is this Michael Ellis?"
    det "¿Mickey? ¿Se trata de Michael Ellis?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:135
translate spanish jez10_718b2d1d:

    # pc "I'm not sure. Maybe."
    pc "No estoy segura. Quizás."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:136
translate spanish jez10_622f048c:

    # det "Lives in a trailer west of town, with his mom and a pretty sister named Reba?"
    det "¿Vive en una caravana al oeste de la ciudad, con su madre y una hermana guapa llamada Reba?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:137
translate spanish jez10_f6c2f59a:

    # pc "Okay, yeah, that's them."
    pc "Vale, sí, son ellos."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:138
translate spanish jez10_c069910d:

    # det "We've had our eye on that family for a while now."
    det "Llevamos un tiempo vigilando a esa familia."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:139
translate spanish jez10_b720a2d7:

    # pc "On the family? Hold on - Reba's not involved with the meth at all. Just Mickey."
    pc "¿A la familia? Espera... Reba no tiene nada que ver con la metanfetamina. Solo Mickey."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:140
translate spanish jez10_e2f28a93:

    # det "You sure about that?"
    det "¿Estás segura de eso?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:141
translate spanish jez10_d3811fb9:

    # pc "Pretty sure, yeah. I've seen her and her brother argue about it. I've talked to her about it. She's not involved in any drugs."
    pc "Bastante segura, sí. Los he visto a ella y a su hermano discutir sobre eso. He hablado con ella al respecto. Ella no está metida en nada de drogas."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:142
translate spanish jez10_678eb1d9:

    # det "Okay. Keep telling your story."
    det "Vale. Sigue contando tu historia."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:143
translate spanish jez10_7a086f5e:

    # pc "Well, Mickey took Reba's truck and she asked me to drive her to where he was so that she could get it back."
    pc "Bueno, Mickey se llevó la camioneta de Reba y ella me pidió que la llevara hasta donde él estaba para poder recuperarla."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:146
translate spanish jez10_abbbcc98:

    # pc "I just stumbled across the information. How I got it isn't really important."
    pc "Me topé con la información por casualidad. Cómo la conseguí no es realmente importante."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:151
translate spanish jez10_5e6c8c41:

    # det "Okay. Keep your secrets for now. Where is this place?"
    det "Vale. Guárdate tus secretos por ahora. ¿Dónde está ese lugar?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:156
translate spanish jez10_2cc585da:

    # pc "There's this turnoff on Highway 84, about 3 miles outside of town, right near mile marker 162."
    pc "Hay un desvío en la autopista 84, a unos 5 km a las afueras de la ciudad, justo cerca del mojón del kilómetro 162."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:157
translate spanish jez10_6ea8536d:

    # pc "You turn down that road - it's barely a road, just a path through the trees really."
    pc "Giras por esa carretera —apenas es una carretera, en realidad es solo un sendero entre los árboles—."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:158
translate spanish jez10_6943a06d:

    # pc "Then there's this cattle gate on the right side. I think they keep it closed unless they're expecting people. You go through that."
    pc "Luego hay una verja para el ganado a la derecha. Creo que la mantienen cerrada a menos que esperen a alguien. Pasas por ahí."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:159
translate spanish jez10_7e8f35b4:

    # pc "It winds through the trees until you get to this place. This bunker. It doesn't look like anything really from the outside."
    pc "Serpentea entre los árboles hasta llegar a este lugar. Este búnker. Desde fuera no parece nada especial."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:160
translate spanish jez10_7871a1e3:

    # pc "But they have guards posted outside of it, and I could smell the chemicals coming from inside."
    pc "Pero hay guardias apostados fuera y pude oler los productos químicos que salían de dentro."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:161
translate spanish jez10_2b0aca5c:

    # det "That's definitely interesting."
    det "Eso es sin duda interesante."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:166
translate spanish jez10_e92e9caa:

    # det "Okay. Thank you for telling me about this. If it's actually the place we're looking for, you've helped me out tremendously."
    det "Vale. Gracias por contármelo. Si realmente es el lugar que estamos buscando, me has ayudado muchísimo."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:167
translate spanish jez10_ac21d1ce:

    # pc "I know there's something going on there at least. I hope it's what you're after."
    pc "Al menos sé que allí está pasando algo. Espero que sea lo que buscas."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:168
translate spanish jez10_ff528d60:

    # det "Me too."
    det "Yo también."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:169
translate spanish jez10_892c632e:

    # det "Okay [pcname]. I'll look into it and let you know what happens."
    det "Vale [pcname]. Lo investigaré y te diré qué pasa."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:170
translate spanish jez10_13c9ecec:

    # pc "Be careful. I know they have guns out there."
    pc "Ten cuidado. Sé que tienen armas ahí fuera."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:175
translate spanish jez10_3cedf4a7:

    # det "Yeah, they're dangerous people. You stay away from it, okay?"
    det "Sí, son gente peligrosa. Mantente alejado de allí, ¿vale?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:176
translate spanish jez10_08551511:

    # pc "You got it."
    pc "Entendido."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:182
translate spanish jez10_d41d8cd9_2:

    # voice 'voices/jez_10_3.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_10_3.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:183
translate spanish jez10_862a970e:

    # det "Okay. Thanks again. I'll talk to you later, okay?"
    det "Vale. Gracias de nuevo. Hablamos luego, ¿vale?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:184
translate spanish jez10_44ea8ace:

    # pc "Okay. Talk to you later."
    pc "Vale. Hablamos luego."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez10.rpy:187
translate spanish jez10_6d2ecc3d:

    # "I hang up and put my phone away. I hope I did the right thing here."
    "Cuelgo y guardo el teléfono. Espero haber hecho lo correcto."

